      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHAPARRAL CHASE (7) showed early speed to race on the pace last start before fading to finish fifth of nine over 1560m at Mackay when sent out at long odds. His last win came over today's shorter trip and dropping 2kg in weight he looks well placed to return to form. OUR TURN NOW (1) finished second two starts back at Townsville but failed to fire last time out when finishing ninth of 12 at this track over 1200m after having made a poor beginning when jumping from the widest gate. Is yet to miss the placings in two starts over this course and distance and with a 2kg claimer taking over the reins has each-way claims. LEASE (3) after jumping from a wide draw raced on the speed and fought on well to finish third of 12 at long odds over 1200m at this track last start. In the mix. SUJEED (5) came home well from 11th of 12 into the turn to finish fourth over 1200m here last start. Trained here and racing over 200m more in distance rates well as a leading chance.",
